      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade specimen that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and it shows. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or door dings to be found. Every panel gap is laser-straight. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats are supple with zero bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV damage, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly with crisp, tactile feedback. Mechanically, this car is flawless. It comes with a comprehensive binder of every service interval performed by master technicians, using only OEM parts. The engine bay is detailed and dry, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. Included are both original keys, the factory tool kit, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. This is, without question, the finest example currently on the market.",
